:name: LiteX + VexRiscv
:description: This script is prepared to run Zephyr on a LiteX SoC with VexRiscv.

$name?="litex"

using sysbus
mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription @platforms/cpus/litex_vexriscv.repl

showAnalyzer uart

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
"""
runMacro $reset
